sections.heading: this state or within the state, defined
sections.text: In this state or within the state means within the exterior limits of the State of Nebraska and includes all the territory within these limits owned by or ceded to the United States of America.SourceLaws 1992, LB 871, ยง 9;R.S.1943, (1996), ยง 77-2702.08;Laws 20
